{"tid":1000500,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"依家美斯算唔算老?個態係咪已經冇以前咁好?","createTime":"2019-01-29T12:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T04:31:50.000Z","uid":66351,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0ed495931a34e4759eccab2b15b6b15371a66f","tid":1000500,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n先唔計今年金球連Top3都冇<br />\n就佢本身踢法去計先<br />\n<br />\n我用老馬 一個成日同佢比較的同國球王去睇<br />\n<br />\n當老馬響86世盃一扭幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而美斯07年都有一扭六<br />\n兩個都響當打之年扭扭樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n15，16年都有一兩次一扭六 偶有靈光出現<br />\n<br />\n但依家美斯踏入三字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地成日見到 <br />\n美斯響度挑高個波 <br />\n上帝視角咁助攻<br />\n<br />\n依個正正就係90年老馬巔峰下滑<br />\n（冇咁撚勁啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲係好勁既）<br />\n89美洲盃 90世盃 所作出既表現<br />\n盤扭大幅減少 過頂挑波助攻居多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪 依家美斯=當年90年代老馬啦？<br />\n咁2022年美斯仲踢唔踢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  35歲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf598a6370f52b52f5a973c5dc36d2dda8f0366f","tid":1000500,"uid":129766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"睇埋歐聯先啦"},{"pid":"22b1d60f4518907bb89b37488ef941f0fd7ab6cc","tid":1000500,"uid":3194,"like":17,"dislike":5,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"美斯勝左唔洗點用出力都夠撚一班普通球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對強隊先出力都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3456d8008b59e5d3f1412c21195cd8a27366b3","tid":1000500,"uid":53278,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"過頭長傳助攻仲難過盤扭"},{"pid":"13d2f22a06808c535c66b03c5e2d2b70fed21dd3","tid":1000500,"uid":66351,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5c3456d8008b59e5d3f1412c21195cd8a27366b3","tid":1000500,"uid":53278,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"過頭長傳助攻仲難過盤扭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"但係挑傳俾人可能就係正正因為 <br />\n體能下降問題<br />\n要知道小白之類的人都係三張開始就以傳代跑<br />\n雖然依家偶有咩上帝viewing angle<br />\n一個變速過兩三個<br />\n<br />\n但當年19號的佢係可以跑到卡卡咁快<br />\n12，13，14年都以突破為主<br />\n<br />\n依家又輪休又傳直塞<br />\n好想佢捱到2022<br />\n而唔係今年美洲盃就結束國家隊生涯"},{"pid":"85505cc5179a30e94320189b417573c449248af3","tid":1000500,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"唔洗留力？"},{"pid":"ada9fb4e278f146c037e56ac3a8ee0c147c88da4","tid":1000500,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"盤扭突破差左<br />\n整體同作用勁左"},{"pid":"354639bc02e17045ab91c01dc91ad5d8fbf98962","tid":1000500,"uid":3454,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"而家唔識扭波了<br />\n個廿粒波都係隊友餵俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23b50e9d3074e473a9adb3cc9ebc982768b7321","tid":1000500,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ada9fb4e278f146c037e56ac3a8ee0c147c88da4","tid":1000500,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"盤扭突破差左<br />\n整體同作用勁左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"真 差咗？<br />\n定 唔出招咋？<br />\n<br />\n依排由華維迪教真心見佢接 傳 接 塞 接<br />\n唔好講扭<br />\n帶波跑都少咗"},{"pid":"9faf556218e6885cd7d5d66ac65065daf9e004ac","tid":1000500,"uid":16217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"都成日一挑三四 你有冇睇"},{"pid":"cf407de577bb145aecbfd880b6d97