係佢最高效既時候<br />\n而家美斯都係一樣 只係位置上係攻中<br />\n再者而家佢重傷一次就等如收山<br />\n一定錫身踢 講到尾都係打份工 收錢收工好過啦"},{"pid":"82f8eef21e8e76d5abfb89b3c64a7894437e064d","tid":1000500,"uid":158853,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"所謂弱左老左<br />\n但放眼全球壇仍然top 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無咩好講"},{"pid":"0022872552e2de9a592bf130218daa305b7bf260","tid":1000500,"uid":160589,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:44:04.000Z","msg":"老左但數據都係歐洲第一"},{"pid":"52dab6e3ac57115db451509c076c282544ee1da3","tid":1000500,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0022872552e2de9a592bf130218daa305b7bf260","tid":1000500,"uid":160589,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:44:04.000Z","msg":"老左但數據都係歐洲第一"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}